Ing '''Kalimpong''' ([[Nepali language|Nepali]]: कालिम्पोङ) metung yang balen talimunduk (''hill station'') kareng [[w:Siwalik Hills|Talimunduk a Shiwalik]] (o Mababang Himalaya) king [[Estadu ampong teritoriu ning India|estadu]] ning [[Albugang Bengal]] (West Bengal), [[India]]. Atiu king {{coor d|27.06|N|88.47|E|}}, at maki tas yang manga 1,247&nbsp;[[metre|m]] (4,100&nbsp;[[foot (unit of length)|pie]]).

